{"tid":200174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【又少一間】製作「扑鱷魚機」日本兒童向街機公司破產","createTime":"2017-04-13T17:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T07:57:08.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc91a1e991ece400bb9bc67657c035a6b1f7e49b","tid":200174,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T17:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/11/32/10113257_548017.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F11%2F32%2F10113257_548017.jpg&h=7f5986f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【橙訊】提起「扑鱷魚機」，相信是不少人的童年集體回憶。不過，這款針對兒童街機巿場的遊戲，亦終離不開巿場環境轉變的殘酷現實，宣佈將會破產。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，原名為「ホープ」(Hope/希望)後來改名為KHP的日本廠商近日傳出破產消息，其欠債總額達12億日圓。<br />\n<br />\n希望公司成立於1952年，早期生產汽車，後轉形出遊戲機。當中在1989年由Namco的石川祝男設計、希望公司製作的「ワニワニパニック」，即「扑鱷魚機」大受歡迎，之後公司乘着這股潮流推出系列遊戲機，令公司在1998年賺得31億日圓的營利高峰。<br />\n<br />\n不過隨著智能機及其他娛樂興起，兒童熱愛的街機亦走向末路，令希望公司以破產告終。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2017/04/12/010056290.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fnews%2Fsystem%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F010056290.shtml&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1gHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=299f2be8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2017/04/12/010056290.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"87785efb74a127f75b056f070f50b008cc3d7102","tid":200174,"uid":105846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T17:41:55.000Z","msg":"童年回億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1997fde0b5f25ce09a68a848b07ee772ed065c2","tid":200174,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T01:29:24.000Z","msg":"轉型失敗？"},{"pid":"11674517c358a8d45b3ff031fcb3408af5c338a5","tid":200174,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T01:32:10.000Z","msg":"第一次聽, 向街機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" c